Write a PHP program to open a text file and print all the data in it.

CODE:
<?php
$filename = "data.txt";

// Method 1: Using file_get_contents() (simplest)
if (file_exists($filename)) {
    $content = file_get_contents($filename);
    echo "<h3>File Content:</h3>";
    echo nl2br($content); // Preserve new lines
} else {
    echo "File does not exist!";
}
?>

OUTPUT:
File does not exist!

